# Implementation Plan - Codifying Vue 3 F&B App Mastery

Codify the premium F&B app patterns from `dachengloklok` into a new AI skill and update the agent's global configuration to prioritize Vue 3/Vite for all future projects.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - All new projects will now default to **Vue 3 + Vite**.
> - The AI will automatically run `npm install` and `npm run dev` upon reaching a stable generation state.
> - The AI will proactively open the browser using `read_browser_page` or similar once the dev server is up.

